                    <msPart xml:id="p2">
                        <msIdentifier/>
                        <msContents>
                            <msItem xml:id="p2_i1">
                                <locus from="3ra" to="28rb"/> 
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7023CommKidanTemHeb">Amharic commentary-introduction to the Kidān za-nagh
          and Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                                <note>Amharic commentary-introduction to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1716Kidanz">Kidān za-nagh</ref>
                                    and <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt</ref>.</note>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.1">
                                    <locus from="3ra" to="9ra"/>
                                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7024CommKidanZaNagh">Beginning of the commentary on the kidān za-nagh.</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="am">በስመ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ኪዳን፡ ዘነግሕ፡ ዘነገሮሙ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ወኃብተ፡ 
                                        ረድኤቱ፡ የሀሎ፡ ምስሌነ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለ<corr resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ም</corr>፡ አ<corr resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ሜን</corr>። 
                                        ጌታ፡ በሕይወተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ሳለ፡ ፫ት፡ ዓመት፡ ከ፫ት፡ ወርኅ፡ ያስተማረው፡ ወንጌል፡ ይባላል፡ ሞቶ፡ ተነስቶ፡ ያስተማረው፡ ኪዳን፡ ይባላል፡ ይሀውም፡ ይታወቅ፡ ዘንድ፡
                                        ቅዱስ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ በገላትያ፡ ክታቡ፡</incipit>
                                    <explicit xml:lang="am"><sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ይትእምርተ፡</sic> ኅቡአትና፡ የከዳን፡ መቅድማቸው፡ አንድ፡ ነው። ከእንግዴህ፡
                                        ወዲህ፡ ትእምርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ቢሉ፡ ወይትእምርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ኪዳን፡ ቢሉ፡ ወይኪዳን፡ ይሔድዋል። ትእምርተ፡ ኅቡዓትም፡ ኪዳንም፡ የጌታ፡ ቃል፡ ስለ 
                                        <pb n="9ra"/>ሆኑ፡ በየፈንታ፡ ይነገራሉ፡ እንጅ፡ እንድ፡ጊዜ፡ አይነግሩም። ነገር፡ ግን፡ ካህን፡ ትእምርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ሳይተረጐም፡ መቅደሱን፡ አይከፍተው፡ ካለ፡ 
                                        ትእምርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ይቅድም።</explicit>
                                    <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                                </msItem>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.2">
                                    <locus from="9ra"/> 
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7025CommTemHeb">Beginning of the commentary on the tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                                    <note>On <locus from="14v" to="27r"/> the rubrics are missing.</note>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="am">በእንተ፡ <sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ትእምርተ፡</sic> ኅቡአት። ኅቡዓትን፡ የመማር፡ ኅቡዓትን፡ የማስተማር፡ ነገር፡ እንዲህ፡ ነው፡ ብሎ፡ አፍዝዞ፡ ተወው። አንድ፡
                                        የኅቡዓትን፡ ዘይቤ፡ ለማውጻት፡ ስለሽሽግ፡ ትእምርት፡ ስል፡ ነው። በአንተን፡ ነገር፡ ሰል፡ ምን፡ ምስክር፡ አለ፡ ቢሉ። </incipit>
                                    <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                                </msItem>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="p2_i2">
                                <locus from="28rb" to="58vb"/> 
                                <title>Explanation of the complete kidān</title>
                                <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">100</citedRange></bibl> an 'explanation of the complete kidān', probably 
                                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2260salota">Ṣalota kidān</ref>. On <locus from="42r" to="44r"/> the rubrics are missing.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="am">ይ፡ ካ፡ ይበል፡ ካህን፡ ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ማለት፡ ክቡር፡ ጽኑዕ፡ ንጹሕ፡ ልዩ፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡ ክቡር፡ ብላችሁ፡ አመስኑኝ፡
                                    ከዚህ፡ ዓለም፡ ሰው፡ ለይታችሁ፡ አለ፡ የዚህ፡ ዓለም፡ ሰው፡ ቢከብር፡ የተጸግዎ፡ ነው፡ እንጅ፡ የባሕርይ፡ ክብር፡ የለውም፡ የርሱ፡ ክብር፡ ግን፡ የባሕርይ፡ ነው። </incipit>
                                <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="p2_i3">
                                <locus from="58vb" to="65v"/><locus from="72r" to="72v"/><locus from="79r" to="80v"/> 
                                <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4014Medan">Admonitions (Mǝʿdān)</title>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i3.1">
                                    <locus from="58vb" to="65v"/><locus from="72r"/>
                                    <title>Part of the admonitions: "If you are reaping"</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="am">ክፍል፡ ዘምዕዳን፡ ስታጭድም፡ ቀርምያ፡ አታጽራ፡ አለ። ቁሞ፡ ሲለምን፡ የለም፡ ቢል፡ እንዴት፡ ድንቅ፡ ይሆን፡ እግር፡ እፀቡ፡ አለ፡
                                    ያ፡ ቀርቶ፡ ለተራበ፡ ባይስጥ፡ እንዴት፡ ድንቅ፡ ይሆን፡ አህያ፡ አጋድሎ፡ ብታይ፡ አጨጭነው፡ አለ፡ ለአህያው፡ ራራቶ፡ ለባለመከራው፡ ሰው፡ አለመርዳት፡ እንዴት፡
                                    ድንቅ፡ ይሆን፡</incipit>
                                <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                                </msItem>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i3.2">
                                    <locus from="72v"/>
                                    <title>Part (of the admonitions): Concerning the beauty of the Creation</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="am">ክፍል፡ ስነ፡ ፍጥረትም፡ አንዲህ፡ ነው፡ እሑድ፡ በመጀመርያ፡ መሬትን፡ ውሀን፡ እሳትን፡ ነፋስን፡ ፈጠረ፡ ከለዚህ፡ ፍጥረታትን፡
                                        ሁሉ፡ ፈጠረ።</incipit>
                                    <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                                </msItem>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="p2_i4">
                                <locus from="66r" to="72r"/> 
                                <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1385Fekkar">Fǝkkāre ʾIyasus</title>
                                <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="p2_i5">
                                <locus from="74r" to="79r"/> 
                                <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2353SibylW">Ṭǝbaba Sābelā</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጥበባ፡ ለብእሲት፡ እንተ፡ ስማ፡ ሳቢላ፡ ወለተ፡ ሕርቃል፡ ርእሰ፡ ኤፌሶን፡ </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                        </msContents>
